<h1>Lazy mount demo</h1>

<p>
  The widget below is far below the fold. With <code>config.lazy_mount = true</code>
  it should not render until the viewer scrolls into it (or the test
  helper calls <code>cfTurnstile.mountAll()</code>).
</p>

<div id="spacer" style="height: 200vh; background: #f0f0f0;">
  Scroll down to find the Turnstile widget.
</div>

<%= form_with url: lazy_demo_path, method: :post, id: 'lazy-demo-form' do %>
  <%= cloudflare_turnstile_tag %>

  <div>
    <%= submit_tag 'Submit lazy form' %>
  </div>
<% end %>
